Sony Restarts Toyosato Factory; Nakata Plant Still Closed, Company Says

-- B y   M a r i k o   Y a s u
-- 
2011-04-11T02:29:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/sony-restarts-toyosato-factory-nakata-plant-still-closed-company-says.html
Sony Corp. (6758)  resumed operations at
one of two plants in  Japan ’s Miyagi prefecture that were halted
because of power outages after last week’s 7.1-magnitude
earthquake.  The Toyosato plant partially resumed operations today,
while the Nakata factory remains suspended due to damage caused
by the April 7 quake, said Yasuhiro Okada, a spokesman for the
company.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Mariko Yasu in Tokyo at 
